Slashstrike stalks toward the base still, finally, after much walking, he 
arrives at the place. He attempts to go in. (You got sheilds up, or do Maxi's 
just pass through em or what.

Thrust had not gotten any answer yet. "Hello?" Getting angered, he decided 
that perhaps he was the only intelligent life on this planet. He sent the 
message on a Predacon frequency, "Hello, I've just crashed on this planet, 
and I'm looking for ANYBODY. Over."
